OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FWes Streeting has resigned from his
OL,7,Frole as health secretary, paving the
OL,8,Fway for a potential challenge to Prime
OL,9,FMinister Keir Starmer.
OL,11,FIn a letter to Starmer, Streeting
OL,12,Fwrote that the PM had "many great
OL,13,Fstrengths that I admire" as he
OL,14,Fdeclared that he had lost confidence
OL,15,Fin his leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FHe wrote that he was "proud" to have
OL,7,Fstood alongside Starmer in the 2024
OL,8,Felections, but described the success
OL,9,Fof Reform UK in last week's local
OL,10,Felections as an "existential threat to
OL,11,Fthe future integrity".
OL,13,FElsewhere, he cited Labour's success
OL,14,Fwith cutting NHS waiting times, and
OL,15,Flisted "austerity, the disaster of
OL,16,FBrexit, Liz Truss, the Covid pandemic,
OL,17,Fthe war in Ukraine and now the war in
OL,18,FIran" as challenges the UK has faced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,F"Where we need vision, we have a
OL,7,Fvacuum. Where we need direction, we
OL,8,Fhave drift," he wrote.
OL,10,FStreeting met with Starmer on
OL,11,FWednesday, in crunch talks that only
OL,12,Flasted 16 minutes.
OL,14,FRead Streeting's letter in full below.
OL,16,FDear Prime Minister,
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThe results are in and I am pleased to
OL,7,Freport that I have delivered against
OL,8,Fthe ambitious targets you set for me
OL,9,Fwhen I became your Secretary of State
OL,10,Ffor Health and Social Care.
OL,12,FToday's figures confirm that we
OL,13,Fsurpassed our waiting times target
OL,14,Fdespite strikes, and that waiting
OL,15,Flists fell by 110,000 in March ` the
OL,16,Fbiggest monthly drop outside of Covid
OL,17,Fsince 2008 ` meaning that we are on
OL,18,Ftrack to achieve the fastest
OL,19,Fimprovement in NHS waiting times in
OL,20,Fhistory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThe only question that matters in
OL,7,Fgovernment is whether we leave our
OL,8,Fsuccessors a better situation than we
OL,9,Finherited. Ambulance response times
OL,10,Ffor heart attacks and strokes are now
OL,11,Fthe fastest in five years. A&E waiting
OL,12,Ftimes are improving, with four-hour
OL,13,Fwaiting figures also the best in five
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FWe've recruited 2,000 more GPs and
OL,17,Fsatisfaction has risen from 60 per
OL,18,Fcent to 74.5 per cent since we came to
OL,19,Foffice. We hit our target of
OL,20,Frecruiting 8,500 mental health staff
OL,21,Fthree years early.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FWe've achieved this at the same as
OL,7,Fbalancing the books for the first time
OL,8,Fin nine years and smashing the 2 per
OL,9,Fcent NHS productivity target by
OL,10,Fachieving 2.8 per cent, which means
OL,11,Fthe investment we're putting in goes
OL,12,Ffurther and that the public can have
OL,13,Fgreater confidence that their money is
OL,14,Fbeing well-spent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FNone of this would have been achieved
OL,7,Fwithout the brilliant leadership team
OL,8,Fof ministers, officials, and special
OL,9,Fadvisers we have established in the
OL,10,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,11,Fand the NHS ` superbly led by Samantha
OL,12,FJones and Sir Jim Mackey, who has been
OL,13,Fa knight in shining armour and a
OL,14,Fbrilliant leader of 1.5 million staff
OL,15,Fupon whom all this success depends.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThe National Health Service is the
OL,7,Fembodiment of all that is best about
OL,8,FBritain and our values. Thanks to our
OL,9,FLabour government, it is on the road
OL,10,Fto recovery: lots done, but so much
OL,11,Fmore to do.
OL,13,FThese are all good reasons for me to
OL,14,Fremain in post, but as you know from
OL,15,Four conversation earlier this week,
OL,16,Fhaving lost confidence in your
OL,17,Fleadership, I have concluded that it
OL,18,Fwould be dishonourable and
OL,19,Funprincipled to do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FLast week's election results were
OL,7,Funprecedented ` both in terms of the
OL,8,Fscale of the defeat and the
OL,9,Fconsequences of that failure. For the
OL,10,Ffirst time in our country's history,
OL,11,Fnationalists are in power in every
OL,12,Fcorner of the United Kingdom `
OL,13,Fincluding a dangerous English
OL,14,Fnationalism represented by Nigel
OL,15,FFarage and Reform UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThis represents both an existential
OL,7,Fthreat to the future integrity of the
OL,8,FUnited Kingdom, but Reform UK also
OL,9,Frepresent a threat to the values and
OL,10,Fideals that have made this country
OL,11,Fgreat.
OL,13,FProgressives across our country
OL,14,Funderstand this threat and our
OL,15,Fresponsibility to confront it, but
OL,16,Fthey are increasingly losing faith
OL,17,Fthat the Labour Party is capable of
OL,18,Frising to our historic responsibility
OL,19,Fof defeating racism and offering hope
OL,20,Fthat Britain's best days lie ahead
OL,21,Fthrough social democracy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThere is no doubt that the
OL,7,Funpopularity of this Government was a
OL,8,Fmajor and common factor in our defeats
OL,9,Facross England, Scotland and Wales.
OL,10,FGood Labour people lost through no
OL,11,Ffault of their own.
OL,13,FThere are many reasons we could point
OL,14,Fto: from individual mistakes on policy
OL,15,Flike the decision to cut the winter
OL,16,Ffuel allowance to the 'island of
OL,17,Fstrangers' speech, all of which have
OL,18,Fleft the country not knowing who we
OL,19,Fare or what we really stand for.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FYou have many great strengths that I
OL,7,Fadmire. You led our party to a victory
OL,8,Ffew thought possible in 2024 and I was
OL,9,Fproud to fight alongside you in the
OL,10,Ftrenches of that campaign. You have
OL,11,Fshown courage and statesmanship on the
OL,12,Fworld stage ` not least in keeping
OL,13,FBritain out of the war in Iran.
OL,15,FBut where we need vision, we have a
OL,16,Fvacuum. Where we need direction, we
OL,17,Fhave drift.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThis was underscored by your speech on
OL,7,FMonday. Leaders take responsibility,
OL,8,Fbut too often that has meant other
OL,9,Fpeople falling on their swords.
OL,11,FYou also need to listen to your
OL,12,Fcolleagues, including backbenchers,
OL,13,Fand the heavy-handed approach to
OL,14,Fdissenting voices diminishes our
OL,15,Fpolitics.
OL,17,FAs a member of your government, I know
OL,18,Fbetter than most that governing is
OL,19,Fhard. It should be, because it matters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FThere are enormous challenges facing
OL,7,Fthis country. For the first time in
OL,8,Four history the next generation faces
OL,9,Fa worse inheritance than the last.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FWe have wars raging in Europe and the
OL,7,FMiddle East that are making our
OL,8,Fchallenges harder, not easier. We are
OL,9,Fin the foothills of a technological
OL,10,Findustrial revolution that has huge
OL,11,Fimplications for every aspect of our
OL,12,Flives ` not least the future of work.
OL,13,FIt is not clear whether democracy or
OL,14,Ftyranny will define the 21st century.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FAfter the financial crisis, austerity,
OL,7,Fthe disaster of Brexit, Liz Truss, the
OL,8,FCovid pandemic, the war in Ukraine and
OL,9,Fnow the war in Iran, the country needs
OL,10,Fto believe again that things can be
OL,11,Fbetter than this and that politics is
OL,12,Fpart of the answer, not the source of
OL,13,Fthe problem.
OL,15,FThese are big challenges that require
OL,16,Fa bold vision and bigger solutions
OL,17,Fthan we are offering.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FIt is now clear that you will not lead
OL,7,Fthe Labour Party into the next general
OL,8,Felection and that Labour MPs and
OL,9,FLabour Unions want the debate about
OL,10,Fwhat comes next to be a battle of
OL,11,Fideas, not of personalities or petty
OL,12,Ffactionalism.
OL,14,FIt needs to be broad, and it needs the
OL,15,Fbest possible field of candidates. I
OL,16,Fsupport that approach and I hope that
OL,17,Fyou will facilitate this.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778832412
OL,3,CIn full: Wes Streeting's resignation
OL,4,Cletter to PM
OL,6,FServing as your Secretary of State for
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care has been the
OL,8,Fgreatest joy of my life and,
OL,9,Fregardless of our differences this
OL,10,Fweek, I remain truly grateful to you
OL,11,Ffor the opportunity to serve and I am
OL,12,Fdeeply saddened to be leaving
OL,13,Fgovernment in this way.
OL,15,FYours sincerely, The Rt Hon Wes
OL,16,FStreeting MP.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
